Class AuditRequestContextPropagatingExecutorService

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.audit.context.AuditRequestContextPropagatingExecutorService
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executor, ExecutorService, ConfigurableExecutorService
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AuditRequestContextPropagatingScheduledExecutorService

    public class AuditRequestContextPropagatingExecutorService
extends Object
implements ConfigurableExecutorService
    ExecutorService decorator that propagates AuditRequestContext from task publishing thread to task consuming thread.

    13.0.0
